How do I schedule a service?",a:"You can request a service through our website or customer portal. Tell us what you need and your preferred timing. We'll match you with the right pro and confirm your appointment."},{q:"Can I reschedule or cancel a service?",a:"Yes. You can reschedule or cancel most services up to 24 hours before the scheduled time at no charge. Some services may have different policies, which we'll clearly communicate."},{q:"What if I'm not happy with a service?",a:"Contact us within 24 hours of the service. We'll either send someone back to fix the issue or provide a credit/refund. Your satisfaction is guaranteed."}]},{category:"For Vendors",questions:[{q:"How do I become a Mercurius vendor?",a:"Apply through our vendor application page. We look for licensed, insured professionals with a track record of quality work. We review applications within 3 business days."},{q:"How does vendor payment work?",a:"Vendors receive weekly payouts via direct deposit. You can track your earnings, completed jobs, and pending payouts in the vendor portal."},{q:"Can I set my own prices?",a:"Mercurius sets service pricing to ensure consistency for customers. Vendors earn competitive rates for each job type, with bonuses for quality and performance."}]}],_ge=()=>{const[e,t]=m.useState({}),n=a=>{t(s=>({...s,[a]:!s[a]}))};return r.jsxs(He,{children:[r.jsx("section",{className:"bg-hero py-16 md:py-20",children:r.jsxs("div",{className:"container-narrow text-center",children:[r.jsx("span",{className:"inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-sage-light text-sage-dark text-sm font-medium mb-6",children:"FAQ"}),r.jsx("h1",{className:"text-foreground mb-6",children:"Frequently Asked Questions"}),r.jsx("p",{className:"text-xl text-muted-foreground",children:"Find answers to common questions about Mercurius."})]})}),r.jsx("section",{className:"section bg-background",children:r.jsx("div",{className:"container-narrow",children:r.jsx("div",{className:"space-y-12",children:Cge.map(a=>r