 Mercurius"}),r.jsx("p",{children:'Mercurius ("we," "us," "our") operates a managed home services platform that connects homeowners in the Fort Myers and Cape Coral, Florida area with pre-vetted local service providers ("vendors"). We coordinate scheduling, communication, quality assurance, and payment processing on behalf of both parties. Mercurius is not itself a contractor or service provider.'})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"2. Acceptance of Terms"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"By accessing or using the Mercurius platform (website, mobile applications, or related services), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use our services."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"3. User Accounts"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"You must provide accurate, complete information when creating an account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity under your account. Mercurius reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms or engage in fraudulent activity."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"4. Services, Booking & Pricing"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"All service pricing is displayed upfront before you confirm a booking. Prices include the service fee and a platform coordination fee. Once a booking is confirmed, the quoted price is locked unless the scope of work changes and both parties agree to an adjustment."}),r.jsx("p",{children:"Cancellations made more than 24 hours before a scheduled service are fully refundable. Late cancellations or no-shows may incur a fee as described in our Reschedule & Cancellation Policy."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"5. Payments"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"Payments are processed securely through our third-party payment provider. By booking a service, you authorize Mercurius to charge the payment method on file. Vendors receive payouts after job completion and homeowner confirmation."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"6. Vendor Relationship"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"Vendors listed on Mercurius are independent contractors, not employees of Mercurius. While we vet vendors for licensing, insurance, and quality standards, Mercurius does not directly supervise or control the work performed. Any warranties or guarantees provided are between you and the vendor, facilitated by our platform."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"7. Service Guarantee"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"We stand behind the quality of work coordinated through our platform. If a service does not meet the agreed-upon scope, contact us within 48 hours of completion. We will work with the vendor to resolve the issue or arrange a re-service at no additional cost."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"8. Photo Documentation"}),r.jsx("p",{children:"Vendors may take before-and-after photos of completed work for quality assurance purposes. These photos are visible to the homeowner and Mercurius staff. By using the platform, you consent to this documentation process."})]}),r.jsxs("section",{children:[r.jsx("h2",{className:"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground",children:"9. Prohibited Conduct"}),r.jsxs("ul",{className:"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1",children:[r.jsx("li",{children:"Contacting vendors outside the platform to circumvent fees"}),r.jsx("li",{children:"Providing false or misleading information"}),r.jsx("li",{children:"Harassing or threatening vendors, staff, or other users"}),r.jsx("li",{children:"Using the platform for any unlawful purpose"}),r.jsx("li",{childr